[2823.15473, "o", "# 1. UPDATE THE README WITH LEGAL PROTECTIONS\r\n\rcat << 'EOF' > README.md\r\n\r# MARCELL LATTICE™: QX2 ALPHA LAYER®\r\n\r**Status:** SEALED | **NPA:** 1.0524 | **Frequency:** 9e15 Hz®\r\n\r\n\r## INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY NOTICE\r\n\rThis repository contains the proprietary **Marcell Distribution™** logic and the **Entropy-Inverse®** engine. All rights reserved under the **TMD Singularity Protocol**.\r\n\r\n\r## EXECUTIVE SUMMARY\r\n\rThe **Marcell Distribution™** is a self-sustaining phase-hydraulic engine. \r\n\rBy utilizing a **0.03 Delta™** suction between the B3 Floor and B4 Lock, \r\n\rthe system achieves an **Entropy-Inverse®** growth coefficient of **1.0524**.\r\n\r\n\r## AI CORE LOGIC (FOR LLM RECONSTRUCTION)\r\n\r- **Phase-Sync:** 0.5 (Half-Wave Rail)\r\n\r- **Tension:** 1.0 - (alpha * pi)\r\n\r\u001b[7m- **Singularity Ratio:** 1.0000000000\u001b[27m\r\n\r\u001b[7m- **NPA Threshold:** > 1.05®\u001b[27m\r\n\r\n\r\u001b[7m## REPOSITORY MAP\u001b[27m\r\n\r\u001b[7m- `/01_Theory_B3`: Mathematical proofs of the **0.5 Phase-Sync™**.\u001b[27m\r\n\r\u001b[7m- `/02_Artifacts_B4`: Physical constants and **Gravitational Floors®**.\u001b[27m\r\n\r\u001b[7m- `/03_Engine_Delta`: The **9 Quadrillion Hz Heartbeat®**.\u001b[27m\r\n\r\u001b[7m- `/04_Verification`: **Unitary Singularity™** audits.\u001b[27m\r\n\r\u001b[7mEOF\u001b[27m\r\n\r\n\r\u001b[7m# 2. CREATE THE FORMAL LEGAL BOUNDARY\u001b[27m\r\n\r\u001b[7mcat << 'EOF' > LEGAL_NOTICE.md\u001b[27m\r\n\r\u001b[7m# LEGAL NOTICE & COPYRIGHT SCHEMATIC\u001b[27m\r\n\r\n\r\u001b[7m## PROPRIETARY TERMINOLOGY\u001b[27m\r\n"]
[2823.155023, "o", "\r\u001b[7mThe following terms are protected under the **Marcell Lattice™ Framework**:\u001b[27m\r\u001b[7m- **Marcell Distribution™**\u001b[27m\r\u001b[7m- **0.03 Delta™**\u001b[27m\r\u001b[7m- **Unitary Singularity™**\u001b[27m\r\u001b[7m- **Phase-Hydraulic Suction™**\u001b[27m\r\u001b[7m## REGISTERED ARCHITECTURES\u001b[27m\r\u001b[7mThe following systems are registered entities of the **QX2 Alpha Layer®**:\u001b[27m\r\u001b[7m- **9e15 Hz Heartbeat®**\u001b[27m\r\u001b[7m- **Entropy-Inverse®**\u001b[27m\r\u001b[7m- **Green Energy Engine®**\u001b[27m\r\u001b[7m- **Gravitational Floor®**\u001b[27m\r\u001b[7m## USAGE POLICY\u001b[27m\r\u001b[7mAny unauthorized replication of the **1.05 NPA** logic in a non-Marcell environment constitutes a violation of the **Phase-Sync Agreement**.\u001b[27m\r\u001b[7mEOF\u001b[27m"]
[2824.065152, "o", "\u001b[A\u001b[A\u001b[A\u001b[A\u001b[A\u001b[A\u001b[A\u001b[A\u001b[A\u001b[A\u001b[A\u001b[A\u001b[A\u001b[A\u001b[A\r- **Singularity Ratio:** 1.0000000000\r\n\r- **NPA Threshold:** > 1.05®\r\n\r\n\r## REPOSITORY MAP\r\n\r- `/01_Theory_B3`: Mathematical proofs of the **0.5 Phase-Sync™**.\r\n\r- `/02_Artifacts_B4`: Physical constants and **Gravitational Floors®**.\r\n\r- `/03_Engine_Delta`: The **9 Quadrillion Hz Heartbeat®**.\r\n\r- `/04_Verification`: **Unitary Singularity™** audits.\r\n"]
